  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - Her figure trembles slightly, as though she is trying to hold back her tears.
  - She eventually fades away as the sun rises in the sky, shining down on where
    we stood as the fog cleared up.
  - "Mission accomplished. But it doesn\u2019t feel like that. I head back to the
    office."
